high_descs: Turn right and move towards the silver range at the end of the kitchen, then turn right and face the small table between trash bag and the kitchen counter.
Pick up the brown egg between the fork and the head of lettuce from the table.
Turn right, towards the blue coffee maker, then turn left and face the sink.
Place the egg in the sink, wash the egg using water from the faucet, then pick up the egg from the sink.
Turn left and move towards the small table in the corner of the room between the trash bag and the kitchen counter.
Place the egg on the top shelf of the table on the edge closest to the red tomato on the kitchen counter.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed egg on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk across the room to the toaster, then turn right and walk toward the head of lettuce on the small side table.
Pick up the egg which is behind the head of lettuce.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the egg in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the small side table.
Put the egg on that table, to the right of the head of lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on a small side table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the black table.
Pick up the egg on the black table.
Step to the right to face the sink.
Place the egg in the sink, wash it, then pick it back up.
Turn to the left and step forward to face the black table.
Put the egg back in it's original position.
anns.task_desc: To clean an egg and put it back in it's spot.
